cyPMCommand.name: cyPMCommand
cyPMCommand.description: A character string for the user to send commands to PM. He can use it to does the save command. Or to list the outlets that need to be turned off, or turned on , or cycled or locked or unlocked as a group. The command is the first word and is followed by a space and the outlet list (otulets commands). Valid commands are 'on', 'off', 'cycle', 'lock', 'unlock', 'save'.

cyPMUnitCurrent.name: cyPMUnitCurrent
cyPMUnitCurrent.description: Current of this PM unit in AMP. The value of this object is the actual current in AMP * 10. You need to translate the readed value (Ex. : value is 5, the current is 0.5 AMP.)

cyPMUnitMaxCurrent.name: cyPMUnitMaxCurrent
cyPMUnitMaxCurrent.description: Maximum current of this PM unit in AMP. The value of this object is the maximum current in AMP * 10. You need to translate the readed value (Ex. : value is 5, the maximum current is 0.5 AMP.)

cyPMUnitSequenceInterval.description: Sequence interval delay. Valid values are 2 to 15 (seconds).

cyPMUnitCycleInterval.name: cyPMUnitCycleInterval

cyOutletName.description: The name given to a particular outlet Maximum size is 8 characters.

cyOutletServer.description: Alias of the Server connected to this outlet .

cyOutletPower.name: cyOutletPower
cyOutletPower.description: Getting this object will return the power state of the outlet. Valid return states are UNKNOW, OFF and ON. Setting this object will change the power state of the outlet.

cyOutletLock.name: cyOutletLock
cyOutletLock.description: Getting this object will return the lock state of the outlet. Setting this object will change the lock state of the outlet.

cyOutletPUInterval.name: cyOutletPUInterval
cyOutletPUInterval.description: The power unit interval of this outlet in seconds. The value of this object is the actual interval in seconds * 10. You need to translate the readed value (Ex. : value is 5, the interval is 0.5 seconds.)

cyOutletMinimumOnInterval.name: cyOutletMinimumOnInterval
cyOutletMinimumOnInterval.description: Minimum time in seconds an outlet will stay on before turning it off.

cyOutletMinimumOffInterval.name: cyOutletMinimumOffInterval
cyOutletMinimumOffInterval.description: Minimum time in seconds an outlet will stay off before turning it on.

cyOutletWakeupState.name: cyOutletWakeupState
